title: It really is that easy! Res Lease in Round Rock. 3 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ['You must see this gorgeous 2-story brick home with 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms in Round Rock, TX just waiting for you!!', 'Nestled in the Oak Creek neighborhood with quick access to Round Rock Ave and Monarch Hwy.', 'The entrance flows into a gorgeous hallway with a luminous living room.', 'Numerous windows allow in tons of natural light making the home so warm and inviting.', 'You will find an ample U-shaped kitchen with plenty of storage with its oak wood cabinets, spacious countertops, and pantry, fully equipped with gas cooktop, dishwasher, oven, microwave and a refrigerator.', "Upstairs there's the main bedroom with carpeted flooring, ceiling-fan, spacious full bathroom, with dual vanity, walk-in shower, garden tub and huge walk-in closet.", "There's also a family living and 2 more bedrooms with 1 shared full bathroom, dual vanity and a bathtub.", 'Additional amenities are the 2 car attached garage and the big private backyard surrounded by threes to enjoy with your loved ones!', 'Tour and apply today, it will lease fast!!', '**', 'In person tours required (No exceptions)', '**', 'All renters are enrolled in the resident benefits package.', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Cristian Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 6979174)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.', 'Listed By: Benjamin Doherty, Sunroom Rentals Texas, LLC']
